    "title": "Entry-Level Fleet Manager at KTC Logistics Holdings Services",
    "description": "KTC Logistics Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Fleet Manager at our Visakhapatnam location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout KTC Logistics Holdings Services:\nKTC Logistics Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with KTC Logistics Holdings Services!",
